video.title: Peixonauta
video.synopsis: Fishtronaut, a water-suit-wearing fish, travels on land to solve mysteries, and helps viewers learn how to protect the environment.

episodes.synopsis: It's a very hot and sunny day at Smiling Trees Park and our trio is really affected by it.
episodes.title: The Case of the Disappearing Picnic Baskets / The Case of the Lost Critter

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek discover a trail of slimy stuff running through the park. What could it be?
episodes.title: The Case of the Yucky Slime/The Case of the Mysterious Honk

episodes.synopsis: Our friends are caught by surprise when the Park's lights don't turn on at dusk as usual and everything is pitch black.
episodes.title: The Case of Mistaken Identities / The Case of the Strange Smell

episodes.synopsis: It's Fishtronaut's birthday and he's very excited at the idea of celebrating it with his friends, but no one seems to have time for him.
episodes.title: The Case of the Oily Rainbow / The Case of the Disappearing Friends

episodes.synopsis: Earth tremors are shaking Smiling Trees Park. Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek are on the case to find out what is causing it. Could it be a volcano?
episodes.title: The Case of the Gopher Frenzy / The Case of the Quaking Park

episodes.synopsis: All of a sudden, gophers are running amok and wreaking havoc in the park. They are disrupting everyone in their frenzy to find new homes.
episodes.title: The Case of the Crabby Birthday / The Case of the Missing Honey

episodes.synopsis: Marina is very focused on playing a mini-game and doesn't even pay attention to Fishtronaut and Zeek when they ask her to help them solve a mystery.
episodes.title: The Case of the Lost Toy / The Case of the Mysterious Spots

episodes.synopsis: It's Fruit Party Week at the park when Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek go on a night adventure.
episodes.title: The Case of the Spooky Night / The Case of Zeek’s Disappearance

episodes.synopsis: When Zeek disappears, along with the candies he was guarding for their party, Fishtronaut and Marina go on an adventure to find him.
episodes.title: The Case of the Sunny Day / The Case of the Long Nosed Monkey

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek are surprised by bubbles in the lake. After investigating, they find that the fish are suffering.
episodes.title: The Case of the Messy Storeroom / The Case of the Pitch Black Night

episodes.synopsis: Marina, Fishtronaut and Zeek go on a mysterious adventure involving a new animal species and a fruit they don't know very well.
episodes.title: The Case of the Flowerless Garden / The Case of the Seven Colours

episodes.synopsis: Our friends are working on a very beautiful project -- planting flowers for a new garden -- but as time passes, the flowers don't blossom.
episodes.title: The Case of the Lazy Rabbit / The Case of the Missing Water

episodes.synopsis: The worksite for the installation of a telescope in the park keeps an owl from getting enough sleep. Marina, Zeek and Fishtronaut speak on her behalf.
episodes.title: The Case of the Stranded Baby / The Case of the Kiwi Bird

episodes.synopsis: Zeek introduces a new friend to Fishtronaut and Marina: a rabbit named Eddy who is a very good runner; no one runs faster than he does.
episodes.title: The Case of the Bubbles / The Case of Happy Plumb

episodes.synopsis: A baby whale gets lost and is now stranded on a sandbank. Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek have to find a way to get the baby back into the open waters.
episodes.title: The Case of the Day that was Night / The Case of the Seed Spreaders

episodes.synopsis: While camping in the park,  Marina, Fishtronaut and Zeek investigate after their tent is hit by a "seed shower."
episodes.title: The Laughter Case / The Case of the Lurking Creature

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek have to find some lilies that are in danger because something is blocking the sunlight from getting to them.
episodes.title: The Case of the Pale Flowers / The Case of the Autumn

episodes.synopsis: Marina, Fishtronaut and Zeek are surprised by the arrival of some mountain sheep by the river.
episodes.title: The Case of the Little Sheep / The Case of the Blue Wings

episodes.synopsis: While Zeek puts on a magic show, our friends see the exact moment when a tree from the Park disappears.
episodes.title: The Case of the Molten Ice / The Case of the Disappearing Logs

episodes.synopsis: Our friends are assigned to a mission and find out that a Spix Macaw got lost from its family when it was just a little blue macaw.
episodes.title: The Case of the Missing Crickets / The Case of the Fluorescent Field

episodes.synopsis: Zeek tells jokes to Fishtronaut and Marina. During Zeek's show, they hear an animal sound they can't identify.
episodes.title: The Case of the End of the World / The Case of the Plastic Bottles

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut, Zeek, Marina and Julia learn about some strange animals that have been brought to the park.
episodes.title: The Case of the Puppies / The Case that Fell from the Sky

episodes.synopsis: A tapir loses its memory and starts acting like a frog. Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek have to find out why this is happening.
episodes.title: The Case of the… What case is this again? / The Case of the Heavy Rain

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut and Zeek have to give Marina a birthday gift, but today is the day and they don't have much time to find out what she would like to get.
episodes.title: The Case of Marina’s Gift / The Case of the Scalding Sands

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek are on a mission to discover which animals from the Park are being fed the wrong kind of food so they can help them!
episodes.title: The Case of the Missing Eggs / The Case of the Disappearing Things

episodes.synopsis: Mac gets lost after going to the hidden part of Adventure Forest alone in search of the rare black orchid without the proper equipment and a map.
episodes.title: The Case of Mac’s Disappearance / The Case of the Three Singers

episodes.synopsis: When the gang saves a tortoise who lands in a tree, they discover a whole new world; two squirrels open a factory that makes natural snacks.
episodes.title: O Caso dos Bichos Desconhecidos / O Caso das Novas Comidas

episodes.synopsis: When Zeek takes over as mailman, everything gets delivered to the wrong places; a TV host decides to do a show about a monster in the park.
episodes.title: O Caso das Entregas Malucas / O Caso do Monstro

episodes.synopsis: A mudslide turns a cave into a tourist attraction that endangers the environment; Zeek sulks when Marina and Fishtronaut find a new friend.
episodes.title: O Caso da Casa que Virou Rua / O Caso do Novo Melhor Amigo

episodes.synopsis: A giraffe takes everyone in the park by surprise when he starts singing; when Marina takes over some chores for the injured Dr. Green, she gets bossy.
episodes.title: O Caso do Animal Silencioso / O Caso do Mistério que Cresce

episodes.synopsis: Zeek struggles with bigger monkeys who steal his bananas and play jokes; a fibbing fish tells tales, but when real trouble comes, no one believes him.
episodes.title: O Caso da Turma dos Bananões / O Caso do Peixinho Mentiroso

episodes.synopsis: All of the animals start copying some little puppies so they can be in style; a parrot hoards bananas and tries to use them as money.
episodes.title: O Caso do Amarelo / O Caso do Tesouro Escondido

episodes.synopsis: Dr. Green leaves Billy and Mac in charge of the park; Zeek helps Marina find her lost tooth so she can put it under her pillow for the Tooth Fairy.
episodes.title: O Caso da Bagunça Bagunçada / O Caso do Dente Perdido

episodes.synopsis: Mac and Billy make major changes to Smiling Trees Park to get it ready for big bike races; Zeek gets a big ego after playing a great basketball game.
episodes.title: O Caso da Alta Velocidade / O Caso do Superzico

episodes.synopsis: The baby animals in the park quarrel over a lucky clover; Zeek searches for a superfood that will make him a superhero and learns a lesson.
episodes.title: O Caso da Briga Boba / O Caso da Frutinha Vermelha

episodes.synopsis: Billy and Mac scramble to solve a mystery involving a mother duck, a mother swan and a missing egg; Billy encounters a lemur abandoned by a circus.
episodes.title: O Caso Ovóide / O Caso do Primo do Zico

episodes.synopsis: A meteor shower in the park blocks the entrance to the home of the burrowing owls; Marina, Zeek and Fishtronaut try to save a blobfish.
episodes.title: O Caso da Chuva de Pedra / O Caso do Peixe Esquisito

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut, Marina, Zeek, Billy, and Mac trace clues to the treasure of the Blue Pirates; Fishtronaut’s cousin looks just like him and wreaks havoc.
episodes.title: O Caso do Navio Pirata / O Caso do Outro Peixonauta

episodes.synopsis: When strange beams of light appear in the park, the turtles worry about their babies; the gang helps a sad stingray whose friends have moved away.
episodes.title: O Caso da Noite Iluminada / O Caso do Deserto Submarino

episodes.synopsis: Marina defends Miss Fox in animal court when Mr. Squirrel loses his winter supply of nuts; the gang must help a lost little Indian boy get back home.
episodes.title: O Caso do Julgamento / O Caso do Indiozinho

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut discovers a highway being built near the park, leading the gang to follow an armadillo's trail; wolf siblings get separated in a storm.
episodes.title: O Caso do Paredão / O Caso da Marina Conectada

episodes.synopsis: A baby zebra, scared of strange noises, and Zeek, suffering from nightmares, both need sleep; a manatee and her new baby must find a safe home.
episodes.title: O Caso do ZZZ / O Caso do Canto Misterioso

episodes.synopsis: Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek try to figure out what's making the park animals all dirty; the gang helps an injured goose fly again.
episodes.title: O Caso da Lata Velha / O Caso do Outono

episodes.synopsis: Dr. Green's research helps a little guinea pig who's been pulled out to sea by the undertow; the worried trio sets out to find the missing Dr. Green.
episodes.title: O Caso da Lua / O Caso dos Golfinhos

episodes.synopsis: Zeek tries to prove how inventive he is, but ends up proving something better; when Dr. Green vanishes, the kids go on a search.
episodes.title: O Caso da Máquina de Fazer Chover / O Caso da Caverna Maravilhosa

episodes.synopsis: Marina and a little bird both must face their fears -- hers of singing in public, and his of flying; Marina's friend from Saudi Arabia visits.
episodes.title: O Caso do Minutinho / O Caso do Rio que Sumiu

episodes.synopsis: Marina’s Saudi Arabian friend helps the gang discover the great value of water; an ultra-deep dwelling fish is lost and needs help to get back home.
episodes.title: O Caso do Quero, quero, quero / O Caso do Peixe Apagado

episodes.synopsis: The gang helps a wild kitty get back to nature when the twins try to adopt it as a pet; when Agent Rosy's recruits vanish, a whale pup saves the day.
episodes.title: O Caso dos Gatos / O Caso do Pequeno Grande Amigo

episodes.synopsis: Zeek plants a new banana grove in secret, but the gang finds out; Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek reunite with Abayomi and help him find his pet bird.
episodes.title: O Caso do Bananal do Zico / O Caso das Asas Amarelas

episodes.synopsis: The gang educates a little elephant who feels jealous over the arrival of a new little brother; a baby panda needs friends to help find his parents.
episodes.title: O Caso do Novo Caçula / O Caso do Preto e Branco

episodes.synopsis: The twins end up fighting over a game of basketball; the mess from a Hawaiian luau leaves a little sand crab trapped in a tuna can.
episodes.title: O Caso das Partes Quebradas / O Caso Havaiano

episodes.synopsis: The gang must solve a mystery to keep a scared mother fox and her babies from moving away; Zeek and his pals help migrating butterflies find shelter.
episodes.title: O Caso da Pedra que Anda / O Caso da Árvore que Voa
